  <brief_title>Procedures, Complications and Follow-up of Tracheostomy in Intensive Care Units.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Procedures, Complications and Follow-up of Tracheostomy in Intensive Care Units - a Prospective Study by Italian Society of Anesthesia, Analgesia, Resuscitation and Intensive Care (SIAARTI)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
